\s1 Some things to do and some things not to do
\p 
\v 12 \w Now|strong="G1161"\w*, Christian friends, \w here|strong="G1722"\w* \w are|strong="G3588"\w* \w a|strong="G2532"\w* \w few|strong="G1722"\w* \w more|strong="G2532"\w* \w things|strong="G3588"\w* \w we|strong="G2532"\w* really want \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w do|strong="G1492"\w*.
\li1 – Respect the people among you that work hard for God. They lead you, his people, and teach you how to live the right way.
\v 13 They work for God, so respect them, and love them a lot.
\li1 – And don’t argue with each other.
\li1 –
\v 14 And the next thing, friends, tell lazy people that they have to work.
\li1 – And if somebody is frightened, talk to them in a way that helps them to be brave.
\li1 – And help anybody that is weak.
\li1 – And don’t get angry with anyone, keep on trying to help them.
\li1 –
\v 15 If somebody does something bad to you, don’t try to do payback to them, but always try to be good to each other and to everyone else too.
